@jd the async PR will amend `retry` decorator to instanciate an async implementation of the controller, reusing the marshaller.

``` python
if asyncio.iscoroutinefunction(f):
    r = AsyncRetrying(*dargs, **dkw)
else:
    r = Retrying(*dargs, **dkw)
...
def wrapped_f(*args, **kw):
